OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy towards the north
OL,6,Fand west with some rain early on and
OL,7,Fagain later in the day. Elsewhere, a
OL,8,Ffine day with plenty of sunshine and
OL,9,Ffeeling very warm in places,
OL,10,Fespecially across the south and east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA band of rain will move
OL,13,Facross Northern Ireland and Scotland
OL,14,Fovernight. Mostly dry for England and
OL,15,FWales with clearest skies in the east.
OL,16,FA mild night away from northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
